<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main>
            <div class="container">
                <section class="about-section">
                    <h1>About Health & Fitness Tracker</h1>

                    <div class="about-content">
                        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                        <p>
                            Health & Fitness Tracker is designed to help individuals monitor and improve their
                            fitness journey. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced athlete, our platform
                            provides the tools you need to track your progress and achieve your health goals.
                        </p>

                        <h2>Features</h2>
                        <ul class="features-list">
                            <li><strong>Activity Logging:</strong> Record various types of fitness activities including
                                running, cycling, swimming, gym sessions, and more</li>
                            <li><strong>Progress Tracking:</strong> Monitor your fitness achievements over time with
                                detailed activity history</li>
                            <li><strong>Search Functionality:</strong> Easily find and filter your activities by type,
                                date range, and other criteria</li>
                            <li><strong>Personal Dashboard:</strong> View all your activities in one place and track
                                your fitness journey</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h2>How It Works</h2>
                        <ol class="steps-list">
                            <li>Create a free account to get started</li>
                            <li>Log your fitness activities with details like duration, distance, and calories burned
                            </li>
                            <li>Search and filter your activity history to analyze your progress</li>
                            <li>Stay motivated by tracking your achievements over time</li>
                        </ol>

                        <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
                        <p>
                            This application is built using modern web technologies including Node.js, Express,
                            EJS templating, and MySQL database to provide a reliable and efficient user experience.
                        </p>

                        <div class="cta-section">
                            <h3>Ready to Start Your Fitness Journey?</h3>
                            <% if (!user) { %>
                                <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register Now</a>
                                <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-secondary">Login</a>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <a href="/add-activity" class="btn btn-primary">Add Your First Activity</a>
                                    <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>